rows.label: qst201316_msg0004
rows.name:
You seem to be from Luxuria. How did
you end up in a place like this?

rows.label: qst201316_msg0005
rows.name:
Um, I... When I came to,
I was lying here...

rows.label: qst201316_msg0006
rows.name:
I was scared and thought I
had to run, but then that
monster attacked me...

rows.label: qst201316_msg0008
rows.name:
I thought bein' "spirited away"
was a joke, but maybe it's real?

rows.label: qst201316_msg0010
rows.name:
For now, let us return to Fons
Maim and report to Dianna.

rows.label: qst201316_msg0012
rows.name:
The chances are slim, but
he might be one of the
kids we're lookin' for.
